* Apply Data Quality\nExpectations
** Declarative Constraints
***_ Validate records in pipeline
***_ Define what valid data looks like
***_ Framework tracks metrics
** Actions
*** EXPECT (default)
****_ Retain invalid records
****_ Track violation counts
*** ON VIOLATION DROP ROW
****_ Remove invalid records
****_ Prevents propagation
*** ON VIOLATION FAIL UPDATE
****_ Stop pipeline
****_ Rolls back transaction
****_ For critical constraints
** Requirements
***_ Requires Advanced edition
***_ Core/Pro editions error out
@endmindmap
